            <thetext>Currently, qx.util.ResourceManager is a static class. It already manages data 
(__registry, __urlPrefix), albeit purely internal, with no external access. 
With the new proposal of adding a real property for URL rewriting to the 
ResourceManager, it seems sensible to turn ResourceManager into a singleton. 
This would also align it with qx.util.AliasManager, which is already a 
singleton.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
