            <thetext>Turned ResourceManager into qx.Class.define, type: singleton; turned static 
methods into instance methods (leaving static data attributes static); static 
methods now issue a deprecation warning and delegate to the instance method; 
changed calls to ResourceManager in the framework, applications and components, 
to use them with getInstance().

